#2001
The Hallway of Movement~
   This is where the art of movement is taught. If you master that already,
feel free to go on. To move around in the world of Elite, there are some
commands to use. You should already know the basics. There are six directions
to go. North, south, east, west, up and down. You can abbreviate those commands
to n, s, e, w etc. To know where you are able to go from one place you can use
the command EXITS. In Elite as in the real world, you cannot always walk to all
the places. There are water, hills and air. Those must be crossed with other
means. Doors and other obstacles may block your way too. There is a sign here. 
