#2002
The Hallway of Scores~
   To keep track of your character here in Elite, there are some scores to show
you the characters statisticts. The most important is the DISPLAY command. It
should show you your Hp, Mn and Mv. Hp stands for Hit points and is a way to
value your health. Try to keep it positive and as high as possible, since
failure will mean death. Mn stands for mana, your mental power. This is most
important for spell casters but all will have use for it. Mv stands for
movement, your endurance in other words. Everything involving movement will tax
your movement, so rest now and then when it gets too low. There is a sign here.

~
